{"tid":1054474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【超級人瑞】日本116歲婆婆獲確認全球最長壽 每早6時起床愛下棋","createTime":"2019-03-09T21:47:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T01:43:00.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2d570fab4cdaeb9e774902851037d4e63917f080","tid":1054474,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T21:47:37.000Z","msg":"日本最老人瑞田中加子（Kane Tanaka）周六獲正式確認為全球在世最長壽的人，儘管她已年屆116歲高齡，但頭腦清晰，每天也會做算術，最喜愛的活動是捉黑白棋。<br />\n健力士世界紀錄職員周六來到福岡市一間安老院中，正式恭喜田中加子成為全球最長壽人士，她的家人以及市長都有到場祝賀。截至今日為止，田中已經活了116年又66天。<br />\n生於1903年1月2日的田中，在家中八兄弟姊妹中排行第七，1922年結婚，與丈夫育有4名子女及領養了另一位孩子。儘管田中曾接受過白內障手術，又曾患大腸癌，但她目前身體狀態良好，在安老院過平靜生活，每天早上6時就起床，下午便研究算術。她最愛的消遣活動是玩黑白棋，更經常擊敗安老院職員呢。<br />\n之前的全球最長壽人瑞是同樣為日本人的都千代（Chiyo Miyako），她去年7月逝世，享年117歲。田中要成為史上最長壽人瑞仍有一段距離，法國女人卡爾芒特（Jeanne Louise Calment）於1997年逝世，享年122歲，至今未有人打破她的紀錄，不過今年初有研究人員聲稱紀錄可能是假的，因為這位「超級人瑞」其實是卡爾芒特的女兒，而兩人都沒有活過百歲。<br />\n《健力士世界紀錄》目前仍在調查全球最高齡男性的頭銜誰屬，去年被確認為全球最長壽男士、居住在日本北海道的野中正造，今年初凌晨在家中逝世，享年113歲。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190309/large/1552118696_2899.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190309%2Flarge%2F1552118696_2899.jpg&h=1d7ef50c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190309/large/1552116572_2358.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190309%2Flarge%2F1552116572_2358.jpg&h=f5dd5eb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左照片：田中加子（左二）與家人合照；右照片：田中加子（右一）與兄弟姊妹合照<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190309/large/1552116383_43b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190309%2Flarge%2F1552116383_43b2.jpg&h=33631d00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n田中加子（前排正中）與兄弟姊妹<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190309/59348883\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190309%2F59348883&d=hArt0m4UYatnQvENVNvF2FEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=55ff39c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190309%2F59348883&h=ba88b1e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190309/59348883</a>"},{"pid":"d20e5bbc2c1a501d6227ad817dba268b0e1a27c0","tid":1054474,"uid":44175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T21:56:53.000Z","msg":"呢啲人瑞對生命嘅睇法會係點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38011f38104fc085e2869cfaf9ecbd4472047406","tid":1054474,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T22:18:51.000Z","msg":"加子定係力子"},{"pid":"b9db8d9693b0e21db4150dd83a674f06fffa9af0","tid":1054474,"uid":30253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38011f38104fc085e2869cfaf9ecbd4472047406","tid":1054474,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T22:18:51.000Z","msg":"加子定係力子"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T22:23:27.000Z","msg":"片假名個カ嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同加同音都係讀ka"},{"pid":"15f13ed6d7d9e29abaf8addb7ee9694d530f30b5","tid":1054474,"uid":130575,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T00:51:46.000Z","msg":"等睇人睇錯每朝6時起床做愛"},{"pid":"99097f40f87f9464b1109b52131a214bd0656527","tid":1054474,"uid":180576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T01:43:00.000Z","msg":"成家都好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}